title: 50 Pack Professional Podiatry Emery Boards for Nails – Reinforced, Durable & Lightweight – Dual Grit Precision Nail Buffers | Acrylic, Gel & Natural Nails
features: Reinforced for Durability – Designed with expert feedback, these wooden emery boards are strengthened for superior reliability while remaining lightweight for easy storage and transport.

Dual-Grit for Precision – Features two different grit levels to ensure a smoother, more refined nail finish, catering to various filing needs. Excellent for buffering and finishing gel, acrylic and natural nails.
Rigid & Strong Build – Unlike reusable steel files that require intensive cleaning, these disposable emery boards provide a hassle-free, hygienic solution for podiatrists.
Color-Coded for Easy Use – Instantly identify the correct grit side with the convenient color-coded design, allowing for efficient and accurate nail filing.
Designed for Podiatrists – Engineered to meet the specific needs of foot care professionals, offering an effective and cost-efficient solution for precise nail shaping and finishing.
description: Professional Wooden Emery Boards for Podiatry – Durable, Dual-Grit, and Color-Coded for Precision Designed using feedback from experienced clinicians, these reinforced wooden emery boards offer unbeatable reliability while remaining lightweight and easy to store or transport. Unlike reusable steel files that require intensive cleaning, these single-use rigid and strong emery boards provide a hygienic and hassle-free alternative. Dual Grit For Acrylic, Gel & Natural Nail Care Each file features two grit levels, allowing for precise and smooth nail finishing tailored to different needs. The color-coded design makes it easy to identify the correct side at a glance, ensuring efficient and effective use. Podiatry Grade Emery Boards Perfectly suited for podiatrists and foot care professionals, these emery boards deliver enhanced results at a cost-effective price point. Whether for clinical or personal use, they provide the perfect balance of strength, precision, and convenience.
